    <detaileddescription>
<para>sqlpp23 table models for the SQL catalog&apos;s backing tables.</para>
<para>These mirror the hand-written shape that sqlpp23&apos;s <computeroutput>ddl2cpp</computeroutput> generator would produce. The schema is compatible with the <ref refid="namespaceApache" kindref="compound">Apache</ref> Iceberg Java <computeroutput>JdbcCatalog</computeroutput>: <computeroutput>iceberg_tables</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>iceberg_namespace_properties</computeroutput>, both scoped by a <computeroutput>catalog_name</computeroutput> column.</para>
<para>This is an internal header: it pulls in sqlpp23 and is only included by the built-in store implementations, never by public catalog headers. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
